                    <span>If you've admired Tiger as a golfer, wait til you read his father's account of how he got that way.  What a great tribute to the parent/child relationship...a powerful reminder that respect between parents and their children is earned, not given.  Also, terrific advice on how to teach your kid to golf at an early age, and wonderful pictures of Tiger and his family</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Watch Tiger on TV - don't buy the book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>2</span>
